title: Wrecked Season 2 Complete 720p HDTV x264 [i_c]
description:
Wrecked is a single-camera comedy. Described as Lost meets It's Always Sunny In Philadelphia, Wrecked follows a group of extremely diverse survivors of a plane crash on a remote island who must adjust to life in a dangerous new world that poses unique threats--mostly brought upon themselves. 
No longer plugged in, the group must navigate this new society and learn to live without the comforts of 2015 like social media, Wi-Fi, indoor plumbing, and Chipotle
